{"tid":1919022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"有線去信鄧炳強追究記者被推跌事件","createTime":"2020-03-10T13:20:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-10T13:28:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2ba8759fc977d03782a9187d1a347cf3b51f1aa1","tid":1919022,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞去信鄧炳強促主動查記者被推跌事件】<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞一名記者前日在將軍澳採訪期間被警員推跌，警方未有透露有關警員身份。有線新聞表示，已去信警務處處長鄧炳強，要求警方主動調查事件及公開調查結果。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞在信中表示，根據警察公共關係科初步了解，指涉事警務人員是不慎撞倒記者，但公司認為現場片段未能支持有關結論，因此要求警方主動及深入調查，以事實回應質疑，又希望警方可提供涉事警員身分。<br />\n<br />\n（PSHK提供）<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #有線新聞 #鄧炳強 #香港警察"},{"pid":"d9c1f1afcc1490328512207531ac2576aeb431f9","tid":1919022,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d4899ae8609ce6ea105a0eec7e1f3cd93235b6","tid":1919022,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"f22e96c3e9f2872b37e800443254fdceb9431a57","tid":1919022,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9c1f1afcc1490328512207531ac2576aeb431f9","tid":1919022,"uid":392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T13:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4eab746a5f424a4cff939631c8273b13d1738b","tid":191